description:
Eddie surprised Amy with a special, unusual gift on the air. Bobby talks about how he doesn’t know some of his friend’s real name and it’s frustrating to Caitlin as they put together their wedding guest list. We drew names for our Christmas gift exchange. Lunchbox prank calls a place to set up a couple’s colonic for him and his wife.
